videoSnippet.title: I Played a Tal Move.... or so I Thought :)
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator I'm reading a book about Tal and I was really inspired to go for a wild attack this game... unfortunately, it backfired :)

1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 Bg7 4. Nf3 O-O 5. h3 d6 6. e4 Nc6 7. d5 Nb8 8. Bd3 Re8 9. O-O Nbd7 10. Rb1 a5 11. Re1 e6 12. Be3 exd5 13. cxd5 Nh5 14. Qc2 Ne5 15. Nxe5 Bxe5 16. Nb5 Qh4 17. Kf1 Bh2 18. Nxc7 Bxh3 19. Nxe8 Bg4 20. Be2 Rxe8 21. Bxg4 Qxg4 22. Bh6 Rc8 23. Qd3 Bf4 24. Bxf4 Qxf4 25. Qe3 Qh2 26. Qh3 Qxh3 27. gxh3 Nf4 28. Rbc1 Re8 29. Rc7  ...
